Cell phone not included.</li><li>Note: This Micro USB 2.0 charger / cable is also compatible with the device with the Micro USB 3.0 port such as Samsung Galaxy Note 3; Please kindly connect this Micro USB 2.0 accessory to the right slot of the connector</li></ul><hr><ul><li><b>Micro USB Noodle Cable</b></li><li><b><font color='red'>NOT compatible with: Barnes & Noble Book Tablet, Nook Color</font></b></li><li>Connect your cell phone to your PC/ laptop to access and synchronize your phone book contacts, emails, and appointments, change ring tones, background pictures, and take advantage of other useful applications</li><li>Supports FBUS, MBUS duplex operation mode</li><li>Supports USB 1.1 and 2.0 connections</li><li>Keep an extra cable handy at home, at work, in the kitchen, and bedroom, etc.</li><li>Cord length: 1 meter</li><li>Color: Black</li><li>Note: Some of the devices might NOT support cable's charging function by the factory setting.
